# Input

```scss
html[lang=#{$locale}]{color:red;}
html[lang=prefix-#{$locale}]{color:blue;}
html[lang="#{$locale}"]{color:green;}

```


# Options

```json
{
    "$schema": "../../../../../../../packages/@biomejs/biome/configuration_schema.json",
    "css": {
        "formatter": {
            "quoteStyle": "single"
        }
    }
}
```

# Formatted

```scss
html[lang='#{$locale}'] {
	color: red;
}
html[lang='prefix-#{$locale}'] {
	color: blue;
}
html[lang='#{$locale}'] {
	color: green;
}

```
